Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:13.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We celebrate our friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:16.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We celebrate the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The memories~ inside~ us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:24.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll build for all to see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The tree brought us together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:32.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And even though it's gone~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:35.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our monument of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:39.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can make the gift live on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:40.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A piece from me~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A piece from you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:46.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll use the tree and we'll~ make do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:48.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If things don't fit~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:50.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's lots of glue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:52.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Friends don't quit in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:55.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And together we'll see this through
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:58.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:02.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To something you hold dear~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:05.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But goodbye isn't fore~ver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:09.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As long as we are here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:16.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The tree is in our memory~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:23.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Its roots have grown deep in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:32.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Its branches raise our spirits, together we're all bound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:36.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forever it stands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:41.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Lost but now it's found
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:43.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So lift a beam~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:45.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And build it strong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Work as a team, it won't~ take long
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hey Silverstream~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:53.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I think that's wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:56.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll live the dream and sing~ our song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:01.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And make the tree something all can see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:08.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In a place where we belong!